---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="SC Driver's License Renewal Guide - Online, Mail, or In-Person" description="How to renew your South Carolina driver's license. Online, by mail, or in-person options explained with fees, requirements, and what to bring.">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold" style="color: #85ccfa;"><img src="/scdmvappt-logo.png" alt="SC DMV Appointments" class="h-10 w-10" />SC DMV APPOINTMENTS</a>
        <nav class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <a href="/guides" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Guides</a>
          <a href="/guides/locations" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Locations</a>
          <a href="/faq" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">FAQ</a>
          <a href="/#signup-free" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-brand-700 transition-colors">
            Get Alerts
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-3">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
        <a href="/guides" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Guides</a>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">License Renewal</span>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Article -->
  <article class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          SC License Renewal Guide
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Three ways to renew your South Carolina driver's license: online, by mail, or in-person. Here's how to pick the best option for you.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Quick Summary Box -->
      <div class="bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-900 mb-4">Quick Summary</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Cost:</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600"> $25 (8-year license)</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">When to renew:</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600"> Up to 6 months before expiration</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Fastest option:</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600"> In-person (same day)</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Easiest option:</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600"> Online (if eligible)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Table of Contents -->
      <nav class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">In This Guide</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#when-to-renew" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">When to renew</a></li>
          <li><a href="#online" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">Option 1: Renew online</a></li>
          <li><a href="#mail" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">Option 2: Renew by mail</a></li>
          <li><a href="#in-person" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">Option 3: Renew in-person</a></li>
          <li><a href="#vision" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">Vision test requirements</a></li>
          <li><a href="#expired" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">What if my license is expired?</a></li>
          <li><a href="#fees" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">Fees</a></li>
          <li><a href="#real-id" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">Upgrading to REAL ID</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <section id="when-to-renew" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">When to Renew</h2>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Your license expires on your birthday</strong> - check the expiration date on your card</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>SC DMV sends a reminder</strong> about 60 days before expiration</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>You can renew up to 6 months early</strong> - don't wait until the last minute</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
            <p class="text-red-800 text-sm">
              <strong>Warning:</strong> There is NO grace period to drive with an expired license in South Carolina. If your license expires, you cannot legally drive until you renew it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="online" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Option 1: Renew Online</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">The most convenient option if you're eligible. Do it from your couch.</p>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900">Renew at scdmvonline.com</h3>
                <p class="text-green-800 text-sm mt-1">
                  Cost: $25 | Delivery: Up to 15 business days
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">You CAN renew online if:</h3>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You're a US citizen</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You have a regular license (Class D, E, F, G, or M)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Your license hasn't been expired for more than 9 months</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You have fewer than 5 points on your driving record (past 2 years)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Your license isn't suspended</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You didn't renew online or by mail last time</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">You CANNOT renew online if:</h3>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You have a CDL (Commercial Driver's License)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You're not a US citizen</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You have a conditional or special restricted license</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">You renewed online or by mail last time (must go in-person every other renewal)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="mail" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Option 2: Renew by Mail</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Same eligibility as online, but you mail a check instead of paying online.</p>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">How to renew by mail:</h3>
            <ol class="space-y-3 text-blue-800 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold">1.</span>
                <span>Write a check or money order for $25 payable to "SCDMV"</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold">2.</span>
                <span>Include your full name, date of birth, and driver's license number</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold">3.</span>
                <div>
                  <span>Mail to:</span>
                  <div class="mt-2 bg-blue-100 rounded p-3 font-mono text-xs">
                    SCDMV<br>
                    PO Box 1498<br>
                    Blythewood, SC 29016-0035
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold">4.</span>
                <span>Mail at least 3 weeks before your expiration date</span>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Same eligibility rules as online renewal. If you can't renew online, you can't renew by mail either.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="in-person" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Option 3: Renew In-Person</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Walk into any SC DMV branch. No appointment needed. Get your new license the same day.</p>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What to bring:</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Your current SC driver's license</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Even if it's expired</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Insurance information</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Know the name of your insurance company</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-4 -mx-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-yellow-900">If your address has changed:</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800">Bring 2 proofs of your new SC address (utility bill, bank statement, etc.)</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-4 -mx-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900">If upgrading to REAL ID:</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-purple-800">Bring all REAL ID documents (see our <a href="/guides/real-id" class="underline hover:text-purple-600">REAL ID guide</a>)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
              <strong>Note:</strong> If you have more than 5 points on your driving record in the past 2 years, you'll need to pass a written knowledge test when renewing in-person.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="vision" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Vision Test Requirements</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            A vision screening is required for all license renewals. Here's how it works:
          </p>

          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">In-Person Renewal</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                You'll take a quick vision test at the DMV. It's just reading letters on a screen - takes about 30 seconds. Bring your glasses or contacts if you need them to see.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Online/Mail Renewal</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Your eye doctor can submit a vision certificate electronically to SC DMV. It must be dated within the last 36 months. Ask your optometrist if they can do this.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="expired" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What If My License Is Expired?</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">Expired less than 9 months</h3>
              <p class="text-green-800 text-sm">
                You can renew normally using any method (online, mail, or in-person). Just pay the standard $25 fee. No tests required.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-2">Expired 9 months or more</h3>
              <p class="text-red-800 text-sm mb-3">
                You must go to a DMV branch in person and:
              </p>
              <ul class="text-red-800 text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>• Bring identity documents (like getting a new license)</li>
                <li>• Pass a vision test</li>
                <li>• Pass a written knowledge test</li>
                <li>• Pass a road skills test</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-red-700 text-xs mt-3">
                Basically, you're starting over as if you never had a license.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
            <p class="text-yellow-800 text-sm">
              <strong>Remember:</strong> Driving with an expired license is illegal in SC. There's no grace period. If you're pulled over, you could get a ticket.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="fees" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Fees</h2>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <table class="w-full text-sm">
              <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                <tr>
                  <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">License Type</th>
                  <th class="text-right p-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Fee</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">Regular license (8 years)</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-right text-gray-900 font-medium">$25</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">REAL ID license (8-10 years)</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-right text-gray-900 font-medium">$25-$28</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">License for age 65+ (5 years)</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-right text-gray-900 font-medium">$9</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-4 text-gray-600">Motorcycle endorsement add-on</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-right text-gray-900 font-medium">$5</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
            Payment: Cash, check, money order, or debit/credit card accepted at DMV branches. Online renewal accepts cards only.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="real-id" class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Upgrading to REAL ID</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Renewal is a great time to upgrade to REAL ID if you haven't already. You'll need to go in-person and bring additional documents.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-3">Documents needed for REAL ID upgrade:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-purple-800 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Proof of identity (passport or birth certificate)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Proof of Social Security number</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
